{"pdfData":[[{"bbox":[98,80,394,91],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"1. 建立图像源，并为OCRMax工具提供您需要对其进行分类的字符的示例图像。","id":"7f95b5e5-08fb-479d-9620-193b665cc8ff","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-0"},{"bbox":[97,94,268,105],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"2. 在显示屏中选择Current.InputImage图像。","id":"a951277e-f8e3-4381-8614-4e1df07307ba","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-1"},{"bbox":[97,111,387,123],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":2,"text":"3. 选择感兴趣区域的图形并对其进行修改以使其紧紧围绕字符串，如下所示：","id":"5aba8691-7480-494c-aa9a-ebab34198bd5","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-2"},{"bbox":[113,131,404,290],"index":4,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/33a1ecefad319417ba47076c2c84204ce6f53b4e425830d614536c58ce8cfca8.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.4890756302521008,"page_idx":0,"id":"9e5ae478-db7b-4a0f-871e-1071267ccebf","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-3"},{"bbox":[96,299,364,329],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"4. 单击“提取行”以使该工具对字符串进行分段并尝试区分单个字符。在大多数情况下，该工具可以正确识别各个字符符号，如下所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"374bccce-7476-415b-b738-fa2c54b365ff","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-4"},{"bbox":[113,338,399,439],"index":6,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/12028e581fd8bc05e72a7266b9726984ba66e61d342e6b8df09f69702081eb58.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.48067226890756304,"page_idx":0,"id":"330cea72-12c0-427f-b671-b9c0f2aee6e6","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-5"},{"bbox":[111,449,463,461],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":7,"text":"在某些情况下，该工具将根本无法执行分割，或者无法正确地正确分割图像，如以下示例所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"99775fdc-e81c-46cd-8388-3d3f75ebac3b","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-6"},{"bbox":[113,469,399,553],"index":8,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/53668c92e4f82602975aeb3f3c0ddc27bffdcf1235347d6f19abc21ef94383ad.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.48067226890756304,"page_idx":0,"id":"48612e3c-26ea-4acb-a536-5b2ce44e1eb0","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-7"},{"bbox":[111,562,500,586],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":9,"text":"如果该工具没有显示任何分割结果，请尝试调整区域图形，并在字符串周围给它半个字符的宽度，然后再次单击“提取线”。在继续下一步之前，该工具应至少能够执行部分分割。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":0,"id":"47440a26-4ef7-4ac0-9209-94fb2dfb6798","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"0-8"}],[{"bbox":[98,79,461,94],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"5. 使用“期望的文本”字段输入区域图形中包含的字符，然后单击“自动分段”。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"8729b22c-941a-42db-882c-bdb3fce9e9b2","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"1-0"},{"bbox":[117,101,479,115],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"“Tune”选项卡应显示分段的字符串，并在每个字符下方带有一个标签，如下所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"835de949-441a-4735-ad31-000000f152d4","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"1-1"},{"bbox":[116,123,472,496],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/4a268ea87557283b610060cf1aa4f4bba899ed04dbae068a9511bd9793068a26.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.5983193277310924,"page_idx":1,"id":"68e2de03-87a1-44a8-958f-2cee70802417","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"1-2"},{"bbox":[114,504,447,518],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"在某些情况下，该工具会生成多次尝试对字符串进行分段的操作，如下所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":1,"id":"92c3abf0-5063-4b66-aaa6-a482106e7c3e","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"1-3"},{"bbox":[122,535,468,724],"index":4,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/195e77a75b69d6fb65284378f0b1fe37de86e9af03120f3fe8db3f69d5f44f06.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.5815126050420169,"page_idx":1,"id":"85044e5e-f403-4ee1-8869-8921232754c4","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"1-4"}],[{"bbox":[114,79,429,92],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"在这种情况下，请滚动浏览结果并选择显示最佳分割效果的结果，然后再继续下一步。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"171cf2cc-4844-44dc-9066-bd7d32a1b6f1","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-0"},{"bbox":[113,99,500,132],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"OCRMax工具使用标记矩形和单元矩形来定义每个字符周围的边界，如主题选择分段参数中所述。如上图所示，分割过程可能无法为所有字符确定这些矩形的最佳尺寸。有关如何使用图形用户界面更改这些矩形的尺寸的详细信息，请参见更改标记和单元矩形部分。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"488e6f0d-db3e-4c4d-b30a-80b7042f9cda","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-1"},{"bbox":[100,140,183,151],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":2,"text":"# 6. 单击添加和调整。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":2,"id":"dd6857c2-b846-49d4-8149-4415ac5fffe4","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-2"},{"bbox":[113,158,495,192],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"这会将图像中的字符添加到当前字体中，训练要使用的字体，并使用自动调整来确定分段参数的最佳设置，以便可靠地在图像中定位字符。“Tune”选项卡以绿色指示属于字体的字符，并显示用于生成分段参数设置的调谐记录，如下所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"398fa8e8-312a-473e-be30-7bd11667f51a","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-3"},{"bbox":[116,200,376,497],"index":4,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/da3f58a75f77319338d3fa2e819c34cca6dee311a3d912124176064df941bb80.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.4369747899159664,"page_idx":2,"id":"0ff7ac06-bb75-4dbf-b45f-b658bd13cf33","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-4"},{"bbox":[117,505,388,518],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"“使用调音数据”部分介绍了如何使用“调音”选项卡中显示的调音数据。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":2,"id":"26408729-e62c-4366-bba4-d95758623ab6","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"2-5"}],[{"bbox":[91,78,312,89],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"7. 获取您希望应用程序能够分类的字符串的另一幅图像。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"8b2a8949-fe0d-4fac-b2cf-61670f3426cd","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-0"},{"bbox":[105,96,414,108],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"该工具可能会识别字体中已经存在的字符，同时以红色显示未知字符，如下所示：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"4bac1db7-ef84-468f-8c7e-9eaed8e10b9f","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-1"},{"bbox":[107,116,400,222],"index":2,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/bc2b1b35d6adfc4fb5ec726e706d2c54b43daeba621c57ad973d072048cb0878.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.492436974789916,"page_idx":3,"id":"2b89b070-0c79-448f-81b7-1692c1e1c472","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-2"},{"bbox":[91,232,381,243],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":3,"text":"8. 点击红色的“？”标签任何未知字符，然后使用键盘输入该字符的名称。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"009f749b-0fbc-418d-809f-02c82d9b66f8","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-3"},{"bbox":[105,251,251,263],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"对图像中的所有未知字符执行此操作。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"9a8077ce-2654-487c-b879-6e7b5a4f33b0","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-4"},{"bbox":[105,269,381,282],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":5,"text":"您还可以选择使用“提取行”字段并输入该字符串中可见的整个字符串。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"619ef84c-e9eb-4330-9ede-8602e590f254","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-5"},{"bbox":[91,289,288,301],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":6,"text":"9. 单击添加和调整将这些新字符添加到当前字体。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"893c700e-9b46-478d-a491-6b75066c8591","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-6"},{"bbox":[88,308,497,332],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":7,"text":"10. 继续获取图像并将新的字符添加到当前字体，直到需要该工具识别的所有字符都显示在“字体”选项卡上：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"7bb2693b-aec2-4fad-87c3-40fd9d2becfc","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-7"},{"bbox":[107,340,357,645],"index":8,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/80c4878216387029fdabcb0e3588803b02b5133ba13f5090b6fee2ce19576982.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.42016806722689076,"page_idx":3,"id":"fbd22363-1c94-4044-82d0-f685d1640bf0","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-8"},{"bbox":[86,665,453,677],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":9,"text":"同一字符的多个实例表明，该字符在各种样本图像中的显示方式有所不同，可能是由于旋转或偏斜所致。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"d7498351-f2cb-430f-bae2-add508d6cd53","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-9"},{"bbox":[86,694,342,705],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":10,"text":"在一系列测试图像上运行该工具，并验证该工具是否提供足够的读取率。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"6022b05d-fb04-4c5b-857a-bfae5e3d3ec5","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-10"},{"bbox":[86,724,461,735],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":11,"text":"您可能需要调整运行参数，例如“接受阈值”和“置信度阈值”，以根据您的生产环境生成所需的读取率。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"0de11e3b-b258-4026-a211-d3a14ac6d922","page_size":[595,841],"block_position":"3-11"}],[],[]],"mergeConnections":[]}